{"tid":2106391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"山東一對新人半裸躺馬路拍「婚紗照」　身後車輛橫越極驚險","createTime":"2020-07-13T10:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T03:30:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3105bfd02cdff0f8dee5e2b9293b0d6337aa82ae","tid":2106391,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"近日山東一對新人為了拍富有特色的「婚紗照」，竟在一家婚紗攝影公司的安排下，半裸裹著床單躺在馬路上拍照。拍攝時新人身後還有車輛來往，險象環生，引起廣泛關注。<br />\n<br />\n內媒報道指，7月11日（上周六），一家婚紗攝影公司的幾名工作人員指揮這對新人橫躺在斑馬線上，當時兩人半裸，僅裹著床單，並躺在枕頭上。為了拍攝，兩人甚至抱著枕頭吃起快餐。<br />\n<br />\n兩人行徑都被附近路人撞見，婚紗攝影公司的工作人員還站在一旁的車輛專用道為新人擋車，但新人身後仍有不少車輛來往，情況相當危險。路人報警後，目前警方已介入該事件。目前，警方已對婚紗攝影公司負責人和兩位當事人依法做出處理，有關部門已責令涉事公司停業整頓。​<br />\n<br />\n這已不是內地首次有新人在馬路上拍婚紗照。去年11月，湖北陽新的一對新人同樣站在斑馬線中間拍婚紗照，身旁站了好幾名工作人員，他們有的拿道具，有的幫忙整理衣服。攝影師為了追求效果，不時地蹲下身子尋找拍攝角度。最終是在路人的報警下，交警趕到才將這一行人驅離。<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n「這是要一起進入愛情的墳墓？」<br />\n「是什麼樣的腦殘會選擇這樣拍照？拍遺照呢？」<br />\n「他們不會覺得很尷尬嗎？」<br />\n「為浪漫不要命。」<br />\n「大車一過，一路走好。」<br />\n「建議直接冥婚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396827616907264.jpeg/3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396827616907264.jpeg%2F3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a143fbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396829340766208.jpeg/NarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396829340766208.jpeg%2FNarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4dfe2d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396815071744000.jpeg/Ww85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396815071744000.jpeg%2FWw85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f80395e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7fqhY0orOXM&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5f81368f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM</a>"},{"pid":"10536de92c6af263495da5cb2712d6f9df5d5121","tid":2106391,"uid":259088,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"借個位 保安局表示已發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持推個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩L完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者<br />\n<br />\n2.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n3.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹爬山 希望他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031146a3644d14e8dd12ce5032df71c49cb7ff14","tid":2106391,"uid":118120,"like":190,"dislike":3,"score":187,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"婚禮本身係好美麗既事<br />\n佢地可以搞到咁冇美感"},{"pid":"4e1642f606b1821bcc26a9318b21f132dd3e834e","tid":2106391,"uid":73092,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"quote":{"pid":"031146a3644d14e8dd12ce5032df71c49cb7ff14","tid":2106391,"uid":11812