hey do chicken right"},{"pid":"7c7e0532059b63ec819bbbe6fdefab7d78e68ad0","tid":2106391,"uid":131917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T00:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7307796b62a918c10fa71634aaed441a1b5e099","tid":2106391,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"未睇相幻想到好美麗佢地先會用生命影......<br />\n成個setting錯到咁...."},{"pid":"516a492dcceed2710587de60f24d58f37d698fc6","tid":2106391,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:18:53.000Z","msg":"嘩 好有創意好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d6b0a03d58de9f9bd16a03ab594c1ad07f9cc9","tid":2106391,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"本身係撞車黨, 所以要係馬路影?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262aa32d765d3b16cf2122a59d7b49a02ffa2367","tid":2106391,"uid":135840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:30:02.000Z","msg":"放上TikTok威威先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d87b1142bd02a66c1b241fd9d93c99726918b1","tid":2106391,"uid":350051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3105bfd02cdff0f8dee5e2b9293b0d6337aa82ae","tid":2106391,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"近日山東一對新人為了拍富有特色的「婚紗照」，竟在一家婚紗攝影公司的安排下，半裸裹著床單躺在馬路上拍照。拍攝時新人身後還有車輛來往，險象環生，引起廣泛關注。<br />\n<br />\n內媒報道指，7月11日（上周六），一家婚紗攝影公司的幾名工作人員指揮這對新人橫躺在斑馬線上，當時兩人半裸，僅裹著床單，並躺在枕頭上。為了拍攝，兩人甚至抱著枕頭吃起快餐。<br />\n<br />\n兩人行徑都被附近路人撞見，婚紗攝影公司的工作人員還站在一旁的車輛專用道為新人擋車，但新人身後仍有不少車輛來往，情況相當危險。路人報警後，目前警方已介入該事件。目前，警方已對婚紗攝影公司負責人和兩位當事人依法做出處理，有關部門已責令涉事公司停業整頓。​<br />\n<br />\n這已不是內地首次有新人在馬路上拍婚紗照。去年11月，湖北陽新的一對新人同樣站在斑馬線中間拍婚紗照，身旁站了好幾名工作人員，他們有的拿道具，有的幫忙整理衣服。攝影師為了追求效果，不時地蹲下身子尋找拍攝角度。最終是在路人的報警下，交警趕到才將這一行人驅離。<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n「這是要一起進入愛情的墳墓？」<br />\n「是什麼樣的腦殘會選擇這樣拍照？拍遺照呢？」<br />\n「他們不會覺得很尷尬嗎？」<br />\n「為浪漫不要命。」<br />\n「大車一過，一路走好。」<br />\n「建議直接冥婚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396827616907264.jpeg/3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396827616907264.jpeg%2F3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a143fbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396829340766208.jpeg/NarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396829340766208.jpeg%2FNarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4dfe2d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396815071744000.jpeg/Ww85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396815071744000.jpeg%2FWw85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f80395e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7fqhY0orOXM&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5f81368f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"佢哋幾時先可以無咁俗"},{"pid":"80eb5a33a82d11968152753b4db5a2f428fd14b1","tid":2106391,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031146a3644d14e8dd12ce5032df71c49cb7ff14","tid":2106391,"uid":118120,"like":190,"dislike":3,"score":187,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"婚禮本身係好美麗既事<br />\n佢地可以搞到咁冇美感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:09:19.000Z","msg":"homeless"},{"pid":"be1af4b52fc5