-14T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"紅白二事一齊攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd32d61bb98743d5e4388c42ffe04e2f7fab406","tid":2106391,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3105bfd02cdff0f8dee5e2b9293b0d6337aa82ae","tid":2106391,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"近日山東一對新人為了拍富有特色的「婚紗照」，竟在一家婚紗攝影公司的安排下，半裸裹著床單躺在馬路上拍照。拍攝時新人身後還有車輛來往，險象環生，引起廣泛關注。<br />\n<br />\n內媒報道指，7月11日（上周六），一家婚紗攝影公司的幾名工作人員指揮這對新人橫躺在斑馬線上，當時兩人半裸，僅裹著床單，並躺在枕頭上。為了拍攝，兩人甚至抱著枕頭吃起快餐。<br />\n<br />\n兩人行徑都被附近路人撞見，婚紗攝影公司的工作人員還站在一旁的車輛專用道為新人擋車，但新人身後仍有不少車輛來往，情況相當危險。路人報警後，目前警方已介入該事件。目前，警方已對婚紗攝影公司負責人和兩位當事人依法做出處理，有關部門已責令涉事公司停業整頓。​<br />\n<br />\n這已不是內地首次有新人在馬路上拍婚紗照。去年11月，湖北陽新的一對新人同樣站在斑馬線中間拍婚紗照，身旁站了好幾名工作人員，他們有的拿道具，有的幫忙整理衣服。攝影師為了追求效果，不時地蹲下身子尋找拍攝角度。最終是在路人的報警下，交警趕到才將這一行人驅離。<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n「這是要一起進入愛情的墳墓？」<br />\n「是什麼樣的腦殘會選擇這樣拍照？拍遺照呢？」<br />\n「他們不會覺得很尷尬嗎？」<br />\n「為浪漫不要命。」<br />\n「大車一過，一路走好。」<br />\n「建議直接冥婚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396827616907264.jpeg/3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396827616907264.jpeg%2F3FeC501SgpoeeyqKoZ0Wi_WlJdvWFGXo8yIXAPMiFwA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a143fbf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396829340766208.jpeg/NarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396829340766208.jpeg%2FNarxMb8RTySHbjctqp0Wce85TYRCtgGPthLGwrYSxsI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4dfe2d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200713/359396815071744000.jpeg/Ww85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200713%2F359396815071744000.jpeg%2FWw85GXm6LEv7NyklwTmBO7FqwmkUJ_r13mlRxt5pUcY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f80395e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7fqhY0orOXM&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=5f81368f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7fqhY0orOXM</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"好核突同低俗的結婚相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c351e601bb8be310dc808e09cdb2fb49048f9431","tid":2106391,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"推 抗爭Mind Map #快閃文宣 #一國兩制已死 #馬格尼茨基人權問責法案 BNO「5+1」 #取回強積金 #721"},{"pid":"8dc19651822ad9db71c88b3281ba477cc74f8fa8","tid":2106391,"uid":179873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"做乜L 姐"},{"pid":"502f6440962ec3a8dabdbe0bdef7449311b07241","tid":2106391,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39d75d27831978d7b81a53f5eaff9009e3c78e1c","tid":2106391,"uid":25367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T23:37:26.000Z","msg":"喺路邊影婚紗相都算<br />\n唔著衫影婚紗相都算<br />\n但食住KFC影係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"其實係KFC PR搞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（純9Up）"},{"pid":"60ae698a3c8bc8ee5f377bc1c57c5205b941878f","tid":2106391,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1041cb4a744b7e0219225b5fbbba8dcf22fa4b21","tid":2106391,"uid":97001,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"031146a3644d14e8dd12ce5032df71c49cb7ff14","tid":2106391,"uid":118120,"like":190,"dislike":3,"score":187,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T10:05:21.000Z","msg":"婚禮本身係好美麗既事<br />\n佢地可以搞到咁冇美感"},"citedBy":